\fs30 \cf0 \ul Recent (right) drawer
\fs26 \ul :
\f1\b0\fs24 \ul \
\pard\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\ql\qnatural

\f0\b \cf0 \ulnone Keep N most recent patterns:
\f1\b0  StarfishX will keep track of this many recent patterns (sometimes referred to as the "Recent Cache", allowing you to go back and save or re-install particularly good patterns. Note that once StarfishX is tracking the specified number of patterns, creating a new pattern will cause the oldest pattern in the cache to be deleted from your hard disk to make room for the new pattern. Also, if you change this setting to a number which is less than the number of patterns already in the Recent Cache, the oldest patterns will be moved to the Trash until only the specified number of patterns remain.\
\

\f0\b Review recent patterns:
\f1\b0  You can select any of the recent patterns in this list to have it loaded into the image well to the right. Information about the pattern (the palette used and the size of the pattern) is displayed below the image. Once you've selected a pattern, you then have the following options:\
\
\pard\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\li740\fi-20\ql\qnatural

\f0\b \cf0 Save...:
\f1\b0  Saves the selected pattern to the name and directory of your choosing. Any pattern you save this way will never be deleted by StarfishX (unless you save over a pattern StarfishX is currently tracking). The original pattern will remain in the Recent cache until you delete it manually or it is forced out by new patterns.\
\

\f0\b Install on:
\f1\b0  This drop-down menu contains a list of all your monitors. Picking a monitor from this list will install the currently selected pattern on that monitor.\
\

\f0\b Trash:
\f1\b0  Moves the selects pattern from your home directory to the Trash. Note that this happens immediately, without any confirmation. Pressing Command-Delete while on the "Recent" tab has the same effect as clicking this button.\
\pard\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\ql\qnatural
